:

*"A on reče: 'Hoću da živim uz tebe zauvek'"(He said: 'I want to live with you forever').
*"Ona mu je znalašću rekla da ne može da se vrati"(She told him wisely that she couldn't come back).
*"Reče mu da je vreme da ode"(He told him that it was time to go).
*"Njegov otac mu je rekao da ne odustaje"(His father told him not to give up).